dc_title_s: The Balkans 1:250,000. Targul Mures, sheet R-36. A.M.S. M506 (G.S.G.S. 4375)
dc_description_s: AMS 2. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. 4375. Alternate title:Targul Mures, Romania. Transverse Mercator projection. Universal transverse Mercator and Danube zone grids. UTM grid added, gradient tints and isogonic data deleted by AMS, 1948. Relief shown by 50 and 100 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. With a Romanian glossary. Corrected from intelligence reports up to Oct. 1944. See index. Library holdings for this set are incomplete.
dc_publisher_s: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1948.
